  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice. These are the app's own gallery captures from the\n     128×64 screen; an on-device shot of it running live would be even better\n     (it's on the Photo Day list). Draft until then. -->\n<p class=\"\">A Flipper Zero app that generates animated patterns in real time on the device's <strong class=\"\">128×64 monochrome screen</strong>. It runs ten gradient families — horizontal, vertical, radial, diagonal, sine waves, interference, checkerboard, noise, spiral — and converts each to crisp 1-bit graphics with <strong class=\"\">Floyd–Steinberg dithering</strong>, evolving the parameters every second at ~30fps.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Dithered radial patterns generated on the Flipper Zero\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-1.png\" alt=\"Dithered radial patterns generated on the Flipper Zero\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-1.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-1.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-1.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-1.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Dithered radial patterns generated on the Flipper Zero\" width=\"1024\" height=\"512\" style=\"--splay-rot:0.61deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1024×512\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Dithered radial patterns generated on the Flipper Zero</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Checkerboard and noise fields\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-2.png\" alt=\"Checkerboard and noise fields\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-2.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-2.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-2.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-2.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Checkerboard and noise fields\" width=\"1024\" height=\"512\" style=\"--splay-rot:1.55deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1024×512\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Checkerboard and noise fields</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Interference and sine-wave fields, 1-bit dithered\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-3.png\" alt=\"Interference and sine-wave fields, 1-bit dithered\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-3.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-3.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-3.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-3.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Interference and sine-wave fields, 1-bit dithered\" width=\"1024\" height=\"512\" style=\"--splay-rot:1.75deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1024×512\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Interference and sine-wave fields, 1-bit dithered</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Diagonal gradients and spirals\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-4.png\" alt=\"Diagonal gradients and spirals\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-4.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-4.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-4.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-4.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Diagonal gradients and spirals\" width=\"1024\" height=\"512\" style=\"--splay-rot:-0.6deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1024×512\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Diagonal gradients and spirals</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"More real-time generative patterns\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-5.png\" alt=\"More real-time generative patterns\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-5.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-5.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-5.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/flipper-generative-art/gallery-5.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"More real-time generative patterns\" width=\"1024\" height=\"512\" style=\"--splay-rot:-0.6deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1024×512\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">More real-time generative patterns</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"\">Making something genuinely <em class=\"\">generative</em> look good in 1-bit on a tiny embedded display is the whole challenge — the dithering is what turns smooth math gradients into something the Flipper's screen can actually render without looking like mud.</p>",
